    title: 'Helix Phase 1: insert editing basics'
    milestone: 'Phase 1'
    status: 'Backlog'
    priority: 'P0'
    size: 'M'
    body: 'Source: HELIX_KEYMAP_TRIAGE.md

Scope:
- Mode switching: esc
- Deletion: C-w, A-backspace, A-d, A-del, C-u, C-k, C-h, backspace, S-backspace, C-d, del
- Character movement: left, right
- Line movement: home

Goal:
Bring Helix insert mode up to the Phase 1 baseline using existing edit commands, especially common deletion and cursor movement keys.'
